## Meanwhile, on the other side of the world in Australia…
Our champion, **Gauthier Bril**, whom we have already talked about, in his tiny boat, continues to prove his expertise in all conditions by becoming World Champion in single-handed Hansa Parafoil sailing!

This is the fruit of:

- 🏅 **his passion and talent**
- 🏅 **his hard work** (even his obsession!)
- 🏅 **his excellent collaborations**, with his training and racing partner Camille and all the coaches and physical, mental, sleep & stress and communications trainers who accompany him voluntarily, namely [Yves JUDIC](https://www.linkedin.com/in/yves-judic-07936029/), [Philippe Morlot](https://www.linkedin.com/in/philippemorlot/), [Véronique POTELLE](https://www.linkedin.com/in/veropotelle/) and [Patrick LESAGE](https://www.linkedin.com/in/patrick-lesage-597b5322/)
- 🏅 **all the structures that welcome him, provide him with a framework and sponsor him, including All Leaders Initiative…**

### His success is true teamwork, and shared pride!

This is not his first success, certainly not his last, and he constantly needs more financial contributions to tackle **his 2026 challenge, the famous [La Boulangère Mini Transat Officiel](https://www.linkedin.com/company/la-boulangere-mini-transat/), no less!**

#### There is still room for many names on his hull and sails!

Individuals, professionals, sponsors of all kinds, be part, according to your means, of this French adventure full of emotion. Support [Gauthier Bril](https://www.linkedin.com/in/gauthier-bril-07936029/), he will repay you!

